Class ArbDepthCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.legacy.plot.transform.ArbDepthCalculator

  • public class ArbDepthCalculator
extends Object
    A class used to help plot hypocenters by projecting them onto a line drawn between 2 arbitrary points on the earth
    Author:
    sid hellman

        Parameters:
        lat1 - - the latitude of corner 1
        lon1 - - the longitude of corner 1
        lat2 - - the latitude of corner 2
        lon2 - - the longitude of corner 2
        width - - how far away from the center line we should allow projections on.
